<https://w3id.org/narn/to/> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A formal ontology defining temporal entities and the relations of Allen interval algebra."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Temporal Ontology"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/> <https://purl.org/dc/terms/created> "2026-03-13"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/> <https://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> <https://w3id.org/people/erdemonal/me> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/> <https://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-19"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/> <https://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespacePrefix> "to" .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/> <https://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespaceUri> "https://w3id.org/narn/to/" .
