<https://purl.org/dc/terms/created> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AnnotationProperty> .
# 
# https://purl.org/dc/terms/creator
<https://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AnnotationProperty> .
# 
# https://purl.org/dc/terms/modified
<https://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AnnotationProperty> .
