# 
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/after
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/after> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/after> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/after> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/before> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/after> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/after> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The primary interval commences strictly subsequent to the conclusion of the secondary interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/after> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "after"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/after> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "follows"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/after> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The interval of Nienor's birth occurs strictly after the conclusion of the Nirnaeth Arnoediad."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/before
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/before> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/before> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/before> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/precedes> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/before> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/before> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlaps> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/before> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The primary interval concludes strictly prior to the commencement of the secondary interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/before> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "before"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/before> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "precedes"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/before> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The interval of Túrin's birth occurs strictly before the interval of Lalaith's birth."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/containsInterval
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/containsInterval> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/containsInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/containsInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/during> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/containsInterval> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/containsInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The primary interval strictly and completely encloses the chronological boundaries of the secondary interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/containsInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "contains interval"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/containsInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "temporally contains"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/containsInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The overarching timeline of the Narn temporally contains the interval of Túrin's time in Doriath."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/during
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/during> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/during> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/during> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/during> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The primary interval is strictly and completely enclosed within the chronological boundaries of the secondary interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/during> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "during"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/during> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "contained in"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/during> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The interval representing the killing of Khîm occurs strictly during Túrin's habitation at Amon Rûdh."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/endsAt
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/endsAt> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/endsAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasInstant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/endsAt> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/endsAt> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/endsAt> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/endsAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Interval> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/endsAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Instant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/endsAt> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/startsAt> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/endsAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The absolute ending instant bounding the conclusion of a temporal interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/endsAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "ends at"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/endsAt> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "ending point"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/endsAt> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The Battle of Unnumbered Tears ends at the precise instant of the final retreat."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/equals
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/equals> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/equals> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/equals> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/equals> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/equals> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ReflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/equals> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Absolute chronological equivalence where two intervals share identical starting and ending instants."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/equals> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "equals"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/equals> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "same time as"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/equals> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The temporal span of the Siege of Nargothrond equals the chronological span of the Fall of Nargothrond."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishedBy
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishes> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Both intervals share identical ending instants while the primary interval commences strictly before the secondary interval begins."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "finished by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "ended by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The overarching timeline of the Narn is finished by the interval representing the death of Turambar."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishes
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishes> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishes> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishes> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishes> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Both intervals share identical ending instants while the primary interval commences strictly after the secondary interval begins."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "finishes"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishes> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "ends with"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/finishes> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The interval representing the death of Turambar finishes the overarching timeline of the Narn."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasInstant
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasInstant> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasInstant> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasInstant> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasInstant> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Interval> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasInstant> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Instant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasInstant> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The association between a temporal interval and a specific instant contained within or bounding it."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasInstant> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has instant"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasInstant> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "at instant"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasInstant> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The overarching timeline of the Narn has an instant mapped to the moment of Túrin's birth."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Interval> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Interval> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A topological temporal relation between two distinct intervals."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "interval relation"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "Allen relation"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The relational mapping between the birth of Túrin and the birth of Lalaith constitutes an interval relation."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/meets
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/meets> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/meets> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/meets> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/precedes> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/meets> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/meets> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/meets> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlaps> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/meets> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The ending instant of the primary interval is chronologically identical to the starting instant of the secondary interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/meets> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "meets"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/meets> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "immediately before"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/meets> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The chronological span of the Nirnaeth Arnoediad meets the interval of Húrin's captivity without any intervening gap."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/metBy
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/metBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/metBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/metBy> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/meets> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/metBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/metBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/metBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The starting instant of the primary interval is chronologically identical to the ending instant of the secondary interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/metBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "met by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/metBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "immediately after"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/metBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The interval of Húrin's captivity is met by the conclusion of the Nirnaeth Arnoediad."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursAfter
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursAfter> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursAfter> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursBefore> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursAfter> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursAfter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Instant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursAfter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Instant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursAfter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A temporal relation placing the first instant chronologically subsequent to the second."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursAfter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "occurs after"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursAfter> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "later than"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursAfter> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The moment of Nienor's birth occurs after the moment of Lalaith's birth."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursBefore
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursBefore> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursBefore> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursBefore> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Instant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursBefore> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Instant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursBefore> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursSimultaneouslyTo> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursBefore> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A temporal relation placing the first instant chronologically prior to the second."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursBefore> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "occurs before"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursBefore> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "earlier than"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursBefore> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The moment of Túrin's birth occurs before the moment of Lalaith's birth."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursDuring
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursDuring> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursDuring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Instant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursDuring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Interval> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursDuring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The enclosure of a specific instant strictly within the temporal boundaries of an interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursDuring> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "occurs during"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursDuring> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "within timeframe of"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursDuring> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The precise moment of Khîm's death occurs during the interval of Túrin's habitation at Amon Rûdh."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursSimultaneouslyTo
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursSimultaneouslyTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursSimultaneouslyTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursSimultaneouslyTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursSimultaneouslyTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ReflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursSimultaneouslyTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Instant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursSimultaneouslyTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Instant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursSimultaneouslyTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A temporal relation linking two distinct instants that occupy the exact same chronological position."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursSimultaneouslyTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "occurs simultaneously to"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursSimultaneouslyTo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "at same time as"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/occursSimultaneouslyTo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Two separate observations mapping to the exact same chronological instant occur simultaneously."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlappedBy
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlappedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlappedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlappedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlaps> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlappedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlappedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlappedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The primary interval begins strictly within the duration of the secondary interval and concludes after it."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlappedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "overlapped by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlappedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "partially after"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlappedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Túrin's time at Amon Rûdh is overlapped by the preceding interval of his time among the outlaws."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlaps
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The primary interval begins before the secondary interval and concludes strictly within its duration."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "overlaps"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "partially before"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The interval of Túrin's time among the outlaws overlaps with the beginning of his time at Amon Rûdh."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/precededBy
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/precededBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/precededBy> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/precedes> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/precededBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/precededBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The primary interval commences either strictly subsequent to or exactly at the conclusion of the secondary interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/precededBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "preceded by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/precededBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "happens after"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/precededBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Túrin's journey to Doriath is temporally preceded by the span of the Nirnaeth Arnoediad."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/precedes
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The primary interval concludes either strictly prior to or exactly at the commencement of the secondary interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "precedes"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "happens before"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The span of the Nirnaeth Arnoediad temporally precedes Túrin's journey to Doriath."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/startedBy
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/starts> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Both intervals share identical starting instants while the primary interval extends strictly beyond the conclusion of the secondary interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "started by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "begun by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The overarching timeline of the Narn is started by the interval representing the birth of Túrin."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/starts
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/starts> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/starts> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/intervalRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/starts> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/starts> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/starts> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/starts> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Both intervals share identical starting instants while the primary interval concludes strictly before the secondary interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/starts> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "starts"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/starts> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "begins with"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/starts> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The interval representing the birth of Túrin starts the overarching timeline of the Narn."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/startsAt
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startsAt> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startsAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasInstant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startsAt> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startsAt> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startsAt> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startsAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Interval> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startsAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Instant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startsAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The absolute starting instant bounding the beginning of a temporal interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startsAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "starts at"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startsAt> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "beginning point"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/startsAt> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The chronological span of the Narn starts at the moment of Túrin's birth."@en .
# 
# 
# 
# #################################################################
# #
# #    Data properties
# #
# #################################################################
# 
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDateTime
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDateTime> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDateTime> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDateTime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Instant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDateTime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDateTime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The standardized chronological date and time value of a specific temporal instant."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDateTime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has date time"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDateTime> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "dateTime value"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDateTime> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The instant of publication maps to a specific dateTime value in the standard calendar."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDuration
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDuration> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDuration> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDuration> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Interval> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDuration> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#duration> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDuration> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The absolute temporal length spanned by a defined interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDuration> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has duration"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDuration> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "time length"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/hasDuration> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The interval representing Túrin's time in Doriath has a duration measured in several years."@en .
# 
# 
# 
# #################################################################
# #
# #    Classes
# #
# #################################################################
# 
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/EndingInterval
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/EndingInterval> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/EndingInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Interval> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/EndingInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> _:genid1 .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#someValuesFrom> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/Instant> .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/endsAt> .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Restriction> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/EndingInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An interval bounded by a distinct ending instant but lacking a defined starting point."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/EndingInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "ending interval"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/EndingInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "ending point"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/EndingInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "A historical epoch stretching back indefinitely but concluding at a specific catastrophe represents an ending interval."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/to/EternalInterval
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/EternalInterval> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/to/EternalInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#equivalentClass> _:genid2 .
_:genid2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
_:genid2 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#intersectionOf> _:genid7 .
_:genid7 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> _:genid5 .
_:genid5 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> _:genid3 .
_:genid3 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#nil> .
_:genid3 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> _:genid4 .
_:genid4 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#complementOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/StartingInterval> .
_:genid4 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
_:genid3 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#List> .
_:genid5 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> _:genid6 .
